name: Matador
description:
Matador
Madrid, Spain
2008
giclèe
12"x12" inches

12"x12" = Limited edition of 10
24"x24" = Limited edition of 5

All images are printed with archival pigment ink on museum quality Hahnemühle 100% cotton rag paper.  All images are printed by me and come with a signed and numbered certificate of authenticity.

The quoted dimensions are for the size of paper containing the images, not the printed image itself. Please note that this image is square and will be centered on the page.  All of the prints have a minimum border of .5 inches to allow for framing.
